{"type":"article","id":1897,"title":"诗歌 假如党妈欺骗了你","uid":3542,"topics":[96,172,361],"contents":"假如党妈欺骗了你，<br>\n不要悲伤，不要捉急！<br>\n丧母的日子里须要淡定：<br>\n相信吧，百家的骨灰将被你领取！<br>\n心儿永远向着大局；<br>\n现在却常是忧郁。<br>\n一切都是美帝，一切都将会过去；<br>\n而那九泉下的生母，就会成为亲切的怀恋。<br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/v8CIDmp.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/v8CIDmp.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/v8CIDmp.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a>","date":"2020-04-24","agreeCount":5,"discussionCount":0}